The paper introduces a generative model for local structures, such as patches in an image, and focuses on its effectiveness in classification tasks. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of deep networks and arithmetic circuits, which are common in neural networks (cs.NE) and data structures (cs.DS) research.
